[{"Code":"en","Title":"Low Balance Alert","Slug":"low-balance-alert","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">This feature is in pilot phase only. We are testing with initial merchants before rolling out to GA once usage is proven.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">If you want to be notified when one of your currency balances goes below a specified threshold, use our Low Balance Alert feature.  After a threshold is specified when your balance goes below it Xendit sends you an email to alert you. After the balance goes back above the threshold, for example via a top-up, we also notify you that the balance has recovered. </p><p data-block-id=\"mh1ou0kr-cdbzdt-008\">This feature is useful if you want to keep certain currency balances funded to e.g. process a high volume of payouts, and want to be kept updated about your balance amount without having to log into the Dashboard. </p><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Setup</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-7xa9ej-014\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Request access to this <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/e2076b18-9510-11f0-8fd5-83a1796a189a/Merchant%20Financial%20Group%20(MFG)/Setup%20Low%20Balance%20Alert/page1\" translate=\"no\">Retool</a> from Product and Engineering, in #product-issues.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mh1q7kk4-5ihjgb-041\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Tag @nigel and @candra ricky</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">SLA for config: between 1 - 2 business days hehe</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Enter the merchant’s Business ID and Business Name. </p><ol data-block-id=\"mh1psrw7-harn7q-036\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Any BID regardless whether it is on the local or global dashboard can use this feature if desired.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\"><strong>Note: these alerts will only be sent in production, i.e. they track the merchant’s <u>live</u> balances. This prevents unintended spam to the merchant’s emails for test balances.</strong></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Enter the correct currency for the balance which the merchant needs alerts. Supported currencies: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mh1oy6at-30l103-017\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">IDR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">PHP</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">MYR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">THB</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">VND</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">SGD</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">USD</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">HKD</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Enter the desired balance threshold amount, e.g. ‘2000’. Just enter the amount, you do not need to enter the currency here</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Enter the emails of the recipients who should receive the alerts. More than one email can be entered, separated by semicolon</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Hit ‘Submit’. The threshold is now set for that currency balance!</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mh1ox24q-edou3k-013\"><img data-block-id=\"mh1phj3h-68dcc0-030\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-10-22 154737.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Form for setting up low balance alerts with fields for business details and email.\" width=\"762\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:762px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"ee04624c-463e-46c3-aa64-af6edb5e6e95\">Experience</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh1p3eay-7ip07c-024\">When the currency balance for which the alert is configured goes below the threshold, the specified recipients will receive the alert below via email:</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2ti5i7-1hfjtt-014\">Sender: help@xendit.co</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2ti5qa-7hpt72-016\">Title: ⚠️ Your Xendit Account - Low Balance Alert for [currency] Balance</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2sc9b1-qnj6h1-002\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mh1p4epw-41g2fa-025\"><img data-block-id=\"mh1phj3i-bhw4l6-031\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-10-22 155807.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Alert for low Xendit PHP balance, current balance is PHP 1972.4.\" width=\"654\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:654px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\"></p><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\">After the balance has been restored to above the threshold, the same recipients will receive the following email: </p><p data-block-id=\"mh2th3gt-2naqqc-007\">Sender: help@xendit.co</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2th7j0-5tt712-008\">Title: ✅ Your Xendit [currency] balance is healthy again</p><p data-block-id=\"mh1p51ik-wrlt3o-026\"><img data-block-id=\"mh1phj3i-7x7hr1-032\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-10-22 155813.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Notification of PHP balance recovery with current balance details and transaction readiness.\" width=\"639\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:639px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"b70ec001-6f86-480f-a525-adbb470fd118\">Pricing(?)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh1ptobr-oo2884-038\">We currently do not charge for this feature.</p>","SeoTitle":"Low Balance Alert","Description":""},{"Code":"id","Title":"Low Balance Alert","Slug":"low-balance-alert","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">[OPTIONAL]</p><p data-block-id=\"09a2a4e8-987f-4e08-b299-06966458cf3e\">{{Product name}} is only available in {{country}}, {{country}}, and {{country}}.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">The first paragraph should be a brief summary of what will be covered in this article. Be straightforward. Mention only relevant points. Keep it concise, about 3-4 sentences.</p><p data-block-id=\"40dfd135-a242-4409-91a2-1e653153772b\">Use bullet points to list down features (if any).</p><ul data-block-id=\"65ad46c5-620c-44ce-a241-9864d10ff333\"><li data-block-id=\"3a502032-228e-46a3-853d-a976f7b5b944\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b28e870a-e819-4e36-baa3-fdd1839b3433\"><strong>Feature #1</strong> — description</p></li><li data-block-id=\"31728fce-427e-42a2-95d7-7db5efebcce4\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"955769df-ef5e-4970-a1a7-2b935c10cbf1\"><strong>Feature #2</strong> — description</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0040ee89-b030-47a1-a940-31ff266caae9\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"c0ba3757-b30f-4e41-ad82-453e3ca1623d\"><strong>Feature #3</strong> — description</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Write subsections in H2</h2><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">To add a table, click the + sign on the right side and select ‘Table’.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"708\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:708px;width:708px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">Title</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">Title</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">Title</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\">Row 1</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"b81a7bad-f451-4886-a7ee-62a6f3b236e0\">Row 2</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"a5a015f5-b58d-4808-ab02-d152803a94ad\">Row 3</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"85382ea1-2254-4987-be83-9856cbb06daa\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"f4791891-d660-4c70-8338-ebe394f0bb4a\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"ee04624c-463e-46c3-aa64-af6edb5e6e95\">Inserting media</h2><ol data-block-id=\"ad4fe56f-e803-42bd-9228-ae79256cabd2\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"e8d5a759-0187-40fe-b8a6-8efa0d13feb1\"><p data-block-id=\"819e48ce-9a3c-496c-8ad3-4476c2b720e2\">Click the plus icon on the right to upload your image (you can also copy paste it)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5af2bcbb-c099-4668-ae22-186c0d3c9769\"><p data-block-id=\"08a0a742-fdcd-4c23-a159-7522bdbeabbd\">Once uploaded, select the image, then click <strong>Style </strong>&gt; <strong>Rounded</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"2e66b3ad-e910-4bca-a33b-f1aa9bf97d28\"><p data-block-id=\"eeca9763-917c-4076-8da1-f8293d4ff561\">You can also click <strong>Edit</strong> to highlight certain parts of the screen </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\"><img data-block-id=\"2ab1853e-5d2b-4d17-b220-65d1f5bfcfd5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(4).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(4).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"1f37857f-7456-443d-aca3-147afcbad375\">How to write instructions</h2><p data-block-id=\"385988f4-f224-4dee-9ef4-cc1b6724c27d\">Use numbered steps to write instructions. Highlight specific buttons in bold. No need to add punctuation at the end of each step. If you want to add images, add them after each line of text.</p><ol data-block-id=\"f472865b-728c-4d98-a65e-7f54fcc42df2\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"a51375b4-10ff-4f5e-b4f0-ba5a7e29b79d\"><p data-block-id=\"bde2fe77-8994-454b-b794-e83ec089391a\">Click <strong>Balance</strong> &gt; <strong>Top Up</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"191f12ef-849e-46ad-bde8-15bfad31ea9d\"><p data-block-id=\"91805134-01ff-4d3b-9f57-d6fb611ff808\">Fill in your details</p><p data-block-id=\"741d3e85-dd80-4427-8ccd-1f564de660d5\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8da38e1b-e676-4773-93cc-2d86606aa137\"><img data-block-id=\"7a483302-90bb-417c-8f98-ac36c3c844f5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot%202024-09-12%20at%2015.50.05(1).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-12 at 15.50.05(1)\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\"></p></li><li data-block-id=\"e5fdc74f-e5ca-4e12-8b4a-33319081a70e\"><p data-block-id=\"b9f26407-5d62-48ac-8990-66e30e8e4f7a\">Click <strong>Confirm</strong></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"b70ec001-6f86-480f-a525-adbb470fd118\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Low Balance Alert","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Low Balance Alert","Slug":"low-balance-alert","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">[OPTIONAL]</p><p data-block-id=\"09a2a4e8-987f-4e08-b299-06966458cf3e\">{{Product name}} is only available in {{country}}, {{country}}, and {{country}}.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">The first paragraph should be a brief summary of what will be covered in this article. Be straightforward. Mention only relevant points. Keep it concise, about 3-4 sentences.</p><p data-block-id=\"40dfd135-a242-4409-91a2-1e653153772b\">Use bullet points to list down features (if any).</p><ul data-block-id=\"65ad46c5-620c-44ce-a241-9864d10ff333\"><li data-block-id=\"3a502032-228e-46a3-853d-a976f7b5b944\"><p data-block-id=\"b28e870a-e819-4e36-baa3-fdd1839b3433\"><strong>Feature #1</strong> — description</p></li><li data-block-id=\"31728fce-427e-42a2-95d7-7db5efebcce4\"><p data-block-id=\"955769df-ef5e-4970-a1a7-2b935c10cbf1\"><strong>Feature #2</strong> — description</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0040ee89-b030-47a1-a940-31ff266caae9\"><p data-block-id=\"c0ba3757-b30f-4e41-ad82-453e3ca1623d\"><strong>Feature #3</strong> — description</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Write subsections in H2</h2><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">To add a table, click the + sign on the right side and select ‘Table’.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"708\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:708px;width:708px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"><col style=\"width:236px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"79cb2111-6d35-4d4f-b3f9-a0cedc7f8b38\">Title</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"94353891-c86f-4c57-8867-d76b6b6fbb77\">Title</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9a0629da-e09d-4c68-978a-254df0d98a05\">Title</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"2783a2f5-64bd-4682-b9eb-f2a258919cfc\">Row 1</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"16f58514-cb94-4d72-940e-f52e20ca93a8\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6d5dc5-754e-4406-b1db-6a7c50a80415\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"b81a7bad-f451-4886-a7ee-62a6f3b236e0\">Row 2</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"69a84920-1f6b-4609-aef1-c0168eda3fa7\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"e374ea06-4c42-4b6f-b2f3-c86d113d5bfe\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"a5a015f5-b58d-4808-ab02-d152803a94ad\">Row 3</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"85382ea1-2254-4987-be83-9856cbb06daa\"></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"236\"><p data-block-id=\"f4791891-d660-4c70-8338-ebe394f0bb4a\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"ee04624c-463e-46c3-aa64-af6edb5e6e95\">Inserting media</h2><ol data-block-id=\"ad4fe56f-e803-42bd-9228-ae79256cabd2\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"e8d5a759-0187-40fe-b8a6-8efa0d13feb1\"><p data-block-id=\"819e48ce-9a3c-496c-8ad3-4476c2b720e2\">Click the plus icon on the right to upload your image (you can also copy paste it)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"5af2bcbb-c099-4668-ae22-186c0d3c9769\"><p data-block-id=\"08a0a742-fdcd-4c23-a159-7522bdbeabbd\">Once uploaded, select the image, then click <strong>Style </strong>&gt; <strong>Rounded</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"2e66b3ad-e910-4bca-a33b-f1aa9bf97d28\"><p data-block-id=\"eeca9763-917c-4076-8da1-f8293d4ff561\">You can also click <strong>Edit</strong> to highlight certain parts of the screen </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\"><img data-block-id=\"2ab1853e-5d2b-4d17-b220-65d1f5bfcfd5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(4).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(4).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"1f37857f-7456-443d-aca3-147afcbad375\">How to write instructions</h2><p data-block-id=\"385988f4-f224-4dee-9ef4-cc1b6724c27d\">Use numbered steps to write instructions. Highlight specific buttons in bold. No need to add punctuation at the end of each step. If you want to add images, add them after each line of text.</p><ol data-block-id=\"f472865b-728c-4d98-a65e-7f54fcc42df2\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"a51375b4-10ff-4f5e-b4f0-ba5a7e29b79d\"><p data-block-id=\"bde2fe77-8994-454b-b794-e83ec089391a\">Click <strong>Balance</strong> &gt; <strong>Top Up</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"191f12ef-849e-46ad-bde8-15bfad31ea9d\"><p data-block-id=\"91805134-01ff-4d3b-9f57-d6fb611ff808\">Fill in your details</p><p data-block-id=\"741d3e85-dd80-4427-8ccd-1f564de660d5\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8da38e1b-e676-4773-93cc-2d86606aa137\"><img data-block-id=\"7a483302-90bb-417c-8f98-ac36c3c844f5\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot%202024-09-12%20at%2015.50.05(1).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Screenshot 2024-09-12 at 15.50.05(1)\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"yes\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"\"></p></li><li data-block-id=\"e5fdc74f-e5ca-4e12-8b4a-33319081a70e\"><p data-block-id=\"b9f26407-5d62-48ac-8990-66e30e8e4f7a\">Click <strong>Confirm</strong></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"b70ec001-6f86-480f-a525-adbb470fd118\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"04e567e3-7a10-405e-b6e6-7655a93215e6\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Low Balance Alert","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Alerta de Saldo Bajo","Slug":"low-balance-alert","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"2a8709a5-64d0-4132-a741-948044d1ee69\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><p data-block-id=\"d608427a-29fb-442f-adc8-31eb4ad15138\">Esta característica está solo en fase piloto. Estamos realizando pruebas con comercios iniciales antes de lanzarla a disponibilidad general (GA) una vez que se compruebe su uso.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">Si desea recibir una notificación cuando uno de sus saldos de moneda caiga por debajo de un umbral especificado, utilice nuestra característica de Alerta de Saldo Bajo (Low Balance Alert). Después de especificar un umbral, cuando su saldo caiga por debajo de este, Xendit le enviará un correo electrónico para alertarle. Una vez que el saldo vuelva a superar el umbral, por ejemplo, a través de una recarga (top-up), también le notificaremos que el saldo se ha recuperado. </p><p data-block-id=\"mh1ou0kr-cdbzdt-008\">Esta característica es útil si desea mantener ciertos saldos de moneda financiados para, por ejemplo, procesar un alto volumen de desembolsos (payouts), y desea mantenerse actualizado sobre el monto de su saldo sin tener que iniciar sesión en el Dashboard. </p><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Configuración</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-7xa9ej-014\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Solicite acceso a este <a href=\"https://retool.tidnex.com/apps/e2076b18-9510-11f0-8fd5-83a1796a189a/Merchant%20Financial%20Group%20(MFG)/Setup%20Low%20Balance%20Alert/page1\" translate=\"no\">Retool</a> al equipo de Producto e Ingeniería, en #product-issues.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mh1q7kk4-5ihjgb-041\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Etiquete a @nigel y @candra ricky</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">SLA para la configuración: entre 1 y 2 días hábiles hehe</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Ingrese el ID de Negocio y el Nombre de Negocio del comercio. </p><ol data-block-id=\"mh1psrw7-harn7q-036\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Cualquier BID, independientemente de si está en el Dashboard local o global, puede usar esta característica si lo desea.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\"><strong>Nota: estas alertas solo se enviarán en producción, es decir, rastrean los saldos <u>reales</u> del comercio. Esto evita el envío de spam no deseado a los correos electrónicos del comercio para saldos de prueba.</strong></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Ingrese la moneda correcta para el saldo del cual el comercio necesita alertas. Monedas admitidas: </p><ol data-block-id=\"mh1oy6at-30l103-017\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">IDR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">PHP</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">MYR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">THB</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">VND</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">SGD</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">USD</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">HKD</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Ingrese el monto del umbral de saldo deseado, por ejemplo, &#x2018;2000&#x2019;. Solo ingrese el monto, no necesita ingresar la moneda aquí</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Ingrese los correos electrónicos de los destinatarios que deben recibir las alertas. Se puede ingresar más de un correo electrónico, separados por punto y coma</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mh1ox4lr-ny1wo9-015\"><p data-block-id=\"703c45b8-8927-4d8a-91fa-55301bfe974b\">Presione &#x2018;Submit&#x2019;. ¡El umbral ya está configurado para ese saldo de moneda!</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mh1ox24q-edou3k-013\"><img data-block-id=\"mh1phj3h-68dcc0-030\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-10-22 154737.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Form for setting up low balance alerts with fields for business details and email.\" width=\"762\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:762px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"ee04624c-463e-46c3-aa64-af6edb5e6e95\">Experiencia</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh1p3eay-7ip07c-024\">Cuando el saldo de la moneda para la cual se configuró la alerta caiga por debajo del umbral, los destinatarios especificados recibirán la siguiente alerta por correo electrónico:</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2ti5i7-1hfjtt-014\">Remitente: help@xendit.co</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2ti5qa-7hpt72-016\">Título: &#x26a0;&#xfe0f; Su Cuenta Xendit - Alerta de Saldo Bajo (Low Balance Alert) para Saldo en [currency]</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2sc9b1-qnj6h1-002\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mh1p4epw-41g2fa-025\"><img data-block-id=\"mh1phj3i-bhw4l6-031\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-10-22 155807.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Alert for low Xendit PHP balance, current balance is PHP 1972.4.\" width=\"654\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:654px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\"></p><p data-block-id=\"93344d7a-db59-49e1-8e55-14d0de769c08\">Una vez que el saldo se haya restablecido por encima del umbral, los mismos destinatarios recibirán el siguiente correo electrónico: </p><p data-block-id=\"mh2th3gt-2naqqc-007\">Remitente: help@xendit.co</p><p data-block-id=\"mh2th7j0-5tt712-008\">Título: &#x2705; Su saldo de [currency] de Xendit está saludable de nuevo</p><p data-block-id=\"mh1p51ik-wrlt3o-026\"><img data-block-id=\"mh1phj3i-7x7hr1-032\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Screenshot 2025-10-22 155813.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Notification of PHP balance recovery with current balance details and transaction readiness.\" width=\"639\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:639px;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"b70ec001-6f86-480f-a525-adbb470fd118\">Precios(?)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mh1ptobr-oo2884-038\">Actualmente no cobramos por esta característica.</p>","SeoTitle":"Alerta de Saldo Bajo","Description":null}]